collection.description:
Upload complete. Wake up, Citizen. The road ahead is long, so strap in. A new world awaits us.

Neo Tokyo is a collection of VCs, developers, token founders, and highly proficient builders all gathered in one exclusive area of web3. 
Our calling at Neo Tokyo is to prepare and be well positioned at the forefront of the metaverse revolution, once it inevitably arrives. https://neotokyo.codes
